Updated grab_translations script for new (git) layout.
Many new and updated translations.
Updated Android build tools; added .gitignore
Release Free-4.0.5
Fixed Russian translation.
Release Free-4.0.6
Pull in new translations and release Free-4.0.7
Updated translations.
Ice Cream Sandwich Support; Release Free-4.0.8
Updated Slovak translations.
Backport one_percent hack; release Free-4.1.0
Updated Dutch and Turkish translations; simplified settings page; clarified some text
Release Free-4.1.1 (some time ago).
Add scripts to upload APK for download from project page.
Added Greek translation, updated Dutch translation, release Free-4.1.2
Remove a few drawables from Pro that aren't needed in Free, reduces APK size about 3%
Update version to 5 in preparation for two release versions (post- and pre- v11); use new release keystore location.
Begin preparing for split versions to work better on v11+ devices (like Pro + BlackSquare plugin).
Prefer better location for private repo.
Continue working on version switcher. Test out just including the icons outright under drawable-v11, which actually seems like the best option.  Needs further testing on more devices.
Revert back to 4217ac09e4fb48b9344ddc4bc826ed0cdd056d8d to release updated translations before continuing with version sitcher
Add Lithuanian translation; release Free-4.1.3
Revert back to in-progress version-switcher
Reapply 'Add Lithuanian translation; release Free-4.1.3'
Working on switch_version.sh
Removed all notification icons from actual res/ as they are now stored in the repo in the version switcher.
Actually switch drawables; Have git ignore all drawables that aren't explicitely tracked.
Version switcher seems to successfully swap which icon set is used.
Added .gitconfig
Change version code scheme; increase version and version code.
Clean up switcher a bit; change version code prefix and minSdkVersion in manifest when switching.
Fixed mistake with blacksquare icons
Put hdpi icons in the right place (pull-down icon looks better this way).
Show charging icon as appropriate.
Add mdpi icons for black square plugin.
Use hard link rather than soft link for .gitconfig, so that I actually get the contents of the file under vc.
Don't show the timestamp in notification.
Comment/uncomment portions of code based on /*v11*/ comment during switching; option to show current version.
Allow setting current to none.
(Hopefully) properly handle to/from 'none'.
Exclude indicator icons and track res/drawable* by default.
Fix bug so version switcher can update src when used with Pro, too.
Update changes from Pro version of version switcher.
Updated French, Italian, and Traditional Chinese translations.
Add symlink to version switcher.
Release Free-5.0.0
Updates to Dutch and Polish translations.
Updated API11+ icons to be simply white numbers on translucent rather than white on black.
Release Free-6.0.1
Release Free-6.0.2: Only display valid voltage; use notification priority 'low' on Jelly Bean; make action bar more noticeable grey.
Switched to single build with multiple icon sets, pulled in translations, etc.
Updated launcher icons.
Updated .gitignore to track drawables.
Release Free-7.0.1
Support wireless charging status and cold health status; Release Free-7.0.2
Pull in updated translations; Release Free-7.0.3
Remove unnecessary strings.
Treat upgrade/reinstall as reboot -- which means restarting the Service automatically if it was running\!
Automate one-percent hack; release Free-7.0.5
Fixed strings; actually release Free-7.0.5
Added purge_strings.rb for removing particular strings from all translations.
Fixed bug with wireless charging.
Made one-percent hack even more effecient.
Run Service in Foreground.
Release Free-7.0.6
Ported changes from Pro: Now BatteryBot beta.
Ported changes from Pro: Now BatteryBot beta.
Don't ignore libs/
Cancel update-the-predictor AlarmManager alarm when Service is being destroyed.
Fix crash / NullPointerException when onStartCommand is called with null intent.  Release Free-8.0.1 (Beta)
Added option to show time since last status change rather than estimate of time remaining.  Release Free-8.0.2 (Beta)
Simpler, cleaner notification with text rather than graphic.
Updated translations; released Free-8.0.3 (Beta)
Added option to use system notification layout.
Don't restart Settings screen when changing icon set, as there's no need to in Free.
Simplify settings screen -- no need for four categories with one setting each.
Release Free-8.0.5 (Beta)
Pulled in updated Predictor code from Pro, updated Dutch and Italian translations, released Free-8.0.6 (Beta).
Ported bugfixes from Pro.  Release Free 8.0.7 (Beta).
Bugfix: Last release included a regression where very first run of clean install would cause a force close.  Fix and release Free-8.0.8 (Beta).

Merged in updated PredictorCore from Pro with automagic prediction type and fix to make prediction always in the future, updated Spanish translations, purged some unsused strings; Released Free-8.0.9 (Beta).
Merge changes from Pro; release 8.0.10
Port over app widget and updated translations; release Free 8.1.1
Updated Polish translation; Release Free-8.1.2
Fixed missing string in Polish translation that caused crash when app run in Polish; Release Free-8.1.3.
Updated German translation.
Release Free-8.1.4

Port over from Pro version correct code for retrieving widget ids from system.  Shouldn't actually affect things with only one widget, but better to be synced with Pro, and better in case another widget type is ever added to Free.
Updated contact info; Release Free-8.1.5
Updated launcher icons to use ICS blue rather than the green from the original Oxygen icon.
Changed help category header color, updated links, removed some help sections that aren't particularly helpful to have in-app.  Added initial Arabic translation.
Release Free-8.1.6
Added Arabic translator's name to list.
Extensive updates to Arabic translation. Substantial updates to German and Hungarian translations.  Small update to Polish translation.
Updated widget appearance; Released Free-8.1.8
Fix for crash on devices that report charge as greater than 100%.
Release Free-8.1.10
Updated Turkish translations.
Updat app for Android 5.0 Lollipop.
Release Free-8.2.0
